Excellent question! ğŸ” You're touching on how React magically updates the UI when the data (state) changes.

âœ… Short answer:
Yes â€” when expenses changes, React automatically re-runs (re-renders) any component that uses expenses as a prop.

ğŸ§  Letâ€™s go deeper â€” Step by Step:
1ï¸âƒ£ Initial Render
You have this in your main app:

jsx
Copy
Edit
